<div class="container">
  <div class="row align-items-start" style="border:1px solid red">
    <div class="col-12" style="border:1px solid blue">
      <h3>Login to Book Nest</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row align-items-start" style="border:1px solid red">

    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6" style="border:1px solid blue">
      <form>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="email-login" class="form-label">Email address:</label>
          <input id="email-login" type="email" class="form-control" />
        </div>
        <div class="mb-3">
          <label for="password-login" class="form-label">Password:</label>
          <input id="password-login" type="password" class="form-control" />
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Log In</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="col-12 col-lg-6" style="border:1px solid blue">
      <p>Book Nest is a wonderful community for those who love to read.</p>

      <p>If you don't have an account, don't fret! Signing up is easy.</p>

      <p><a href="/signup">Click here to make your free profile.</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>